later, when Wizards midfielder Chris Klein was brought down hard in 
the box. Preki failed to convert the ensuing penalty kick when 
Thornton deflected his shot off the crossbar. 
</P>
<P>
	Chicago sealed the victory when Roman Kosecki and Andrew Lewis  
fed the ball to Peter Nowak at the top of the Wizards' box. Nowak 
scored to give the Fire a 2-0 lead. 
  	   	
